  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dda\u0daf\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A red notice from the weather",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology has issued a red alert warning of strong winds and rough seas.",
        "Due to the activation of South West Monsoon conditions, the wind speed may increase to 60-70 km/h from time to time in the offshore areas from Puttalam to Pottuvil via Colombo, Galle and Hambantota and the sea areas will be rough to very rough to very rough. The department says.",
        "Also, the announcement issued by the department further states that the sea waves are about 2.3-3.5 meters in the areas mentioned above."
      ],
